1130
01:26:12,676 --> 01:26:13,936
Oh, meu Deus!

1131
01:26:14,856 --> 01:26:16,328
Abre, abre!

1132
01:26:20,370 --> 01:26:21,371
O que é?

1133
01:26:22,108 --> 01:26:24,139
- Dinossauros!
- Onde?

1134
01:26:24,207 --> 01:26:27,707
